SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[number_of_episodes], [f].[OriginName], [f].[Poster], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Trailer], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status], [r].[Id], [r].[CreateDate], [r].[FilmId], [r].[IsActive], [r].[LastModifiedDate], [r].[Rate], [r].[Status], [r].[UserId]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
LEFT JOIN [Reviews] AS [r] ON [f].[Id] = [r].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id]

SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[number_of_episodes], [f].[OriginName], [f].[Poster], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Trailer], [f].[Type], [f].[Year], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [s].[CreateDate], [s].[Description], [s].[IsActive], [s].[LastModifiedDate], [s].[Name], [s].[Status], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Status], [r].[Id], [r].[CreateDate], [r].[FilmId], [r].[IsActive], [r].[LastModifiedDate], [r].[Rate], [r].[Status], [r].[UserId]
FROM [Films] AS [f]
INNER JOIN [Schedule] AS [s] ON [f].[ScheduleId] = [s].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c] ON [f].[CountryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreateDate], [c0].[Description], [c0].[IsActive], [c0].[LastModifiedDate], [c0].[Name], [c0].[Slug], [c0].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [f0].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [f].[Id] = [t].[FilmId]
LEFT JOIN [Reviews] AS [r] ON [f].[Id] = [r].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [f].[Id], [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[FilmId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Id]

2024-10-06 21:39:15.918 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (97ms) [Parameters=[@__year_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__country_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__category_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_3='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_4='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CountryId], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Image], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[number_of_episodes], [t].[OriginName], [t].[Poster], [t].[ScheduleId], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [t].[Time], [t].[Trailer], [t].[Type], [t].[Year], [t0].[FilmId], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[LastModifiedDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[Status]
FROM (
    SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[number_of_episodes], [f].[OriginName], [f].[Poster], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Trailer], [f].[Type], [f].[Year]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    WHERE [f].[Year] = @__year_0 AND [f].[CountryId] = @__country_1 AND EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]
        WHERE [f].[Id] = [f0].[FilmId] AND [f0].[CategoryId] = @__category_2)
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f1].[FilmId], [f1].[CategoryId], [c].[Id], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Slug], [c].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f1]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [f1].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[FilmId], [t0].[CategoryId]

FROM [Films] AS [f]

    WHERE [f].[Id] = [f0].[FilmId] AND [f0].[CategoryId] = @__category_2)

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CountryId], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Image], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[number_of_episodes], [t].[OriginName], [t].[Poster], [t].[ScheduleId], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [t].[Time], [t].[Trailer], [t].[Type], [t].[Year], [t0].[FilmId], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[LastModifiedDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[Status]
FROM (
    SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[number_of_episodes], [f].[OriginName], [f].[Poster], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Trailer], [f].[Type], [f].[Year]

) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[number_of_episodes], [f].[OriginName], [f].[Poster], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Trailer], [f].[Type], [f].[Year]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CountryId], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Image], [t].[IsActive], [t].[LastModifiedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[number_of_episodes], [t].[OriginName], [t].[Poster], [t].[ScheduleId], [t].[Slug], [t].[Status], [t].[Time], [t].[Trailer], [t].[Type], [t].[Year], [t0].[FilmId], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[LastModifiedDate], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[Status]
FROM (
    SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CountryId], [f].[CreateDate], [f].[Description], [f].[Image], [f].[IsActive], [f].[LastModifiedDate], [f].[Name], [f].[number_of_episodes], [f].[OriginName], [f].[Poster], [f].[ScheduleId], [f].[Slug], [f].[Status], [f].[Time], [f].[Trailer], [f].[Type], [f].[Year]
    FROM [Films] AS [f]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [f0].[FilmId], [f0].[CategoryId], [c].[Id], [c].[CreateDate], [c].[Description], [c].[IsActive], [c].[LastModifiedDate], [c].[Name], [c].[Slug], [c].[Status]
    FROM [FilmCategories] AS [f0]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[FilmId]

) AS [t]
